3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - Fountain codes are widely used in network coding, which is a topic related to networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - Fountain codes can be used in the context of social and information networks, for example, in distributed storage systems.
